     * The user explicitly dismissed the prompt.
     */
    case cancelled
    /**
     * The biometric check failed (wrong fingerprint, face mismatch, etc.).
     */
    case failed
    /**
     * No biometric hardware exists on the device, or the platform callback
     * has not been registered.
     */
    case notAvailable
